Photo by The Weeknd on August 16, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, beard and sunglasses.

node.text: Forever grateful to be able to experiment with sounds, try new things with my voice and create music with the people I truly love and respect.  For the last decade every song has been a journey and to be able to continue this journey has been nothing short of a blessing. It’s the only gift I could ever ask for. I’ll be doing it for as long as I can breathe. I love my fans and wouldn’t be here without you. Big day for blinding lights. Multiple songs in the top 20. Thursday turns 10. Caesar turned 4 and the fucking dawn is coming. LET’S GO
